<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para><link linkend="_class_k_t_n_1_1_c_m_e_1_1_cme_g_t5">CmeGT5</link> class represents the 5th Generation CmeHandler. Low latency order template creation; memory pool usage and custom maps and memory management. It provides better, faster, and stronger functionality for handling CME exchange iLink3 Messages. </para>
</section>
